    "If additional searches ended up being iterative and producing results already recorded in the database, the researchers moved on to the next country.",
    "While this database aims to be comprehensive and therefore designed for most inclusive/generic search strings, it is possible that additional searches with additional keywords such as \"ChatGPT\" would produce additional results.",
